4,1821	no little coat rev sylvester judd augusta maine season year has arrived when our mothers like hannah old are making their children little coats dress necessary appendage body constitutes no inconspicuous feature our earthly life wherewithal shall we clothed gentilian question old we are all gentiles still dress becomes exponent mind which its turn more less tinged what we wear children are easily taught love dress they set just about value which their parents friends do their behalf have seen children vain their dresses but they were not half so vain their mothers were them some mothers try exceedingly awaken their very young children sensibility dress so attach them colors finery pains are taken impress upon mind child has something pretty soon learns discriminate such matters passion too sometimes takes precedence love goodness love truly beautiful love nature god once established assumes haughty sway over soul our youths some them become sadly enslaved vice when see young persons devoted dress studious appearances aiming effect more what external than internal obvious reflect their mothers once made them little coats like manner also when see child imitating example yielding impress carrying out principles developing spirit parent am reminded mother once made him little coat we are permitted then leave letter text follow out what may suggest spirit clothing scripture frequently mentioned figurative spiritual sense we are said clothed righteousness clothed shame overcometh shall clothed white clothing stands virtues vices which we may suppose man invested st paul desires clothed upon house which above desires exhibit fair beautiful image perfect christian spirit character may were dressed heavenly love text season year remind me then other things than mere working raw materials rather outward act suggests certain things inward life let me then say brief word parents you are clothing your children honor shame righteousness waywardness you are making them little coats which they must wear long while you are fitting garment white which they shall shine forever kingdom god desolation which sinful soul shall perpetually folded meet man streets literally clothed rags clothed also manifold tokens depraved life asked did not mother when young make him little coat when see person clothed scripture has humility entertaining modest sense himself just estimate others unostentatiously attaching himself great principles meekly waiting will god reverent truth supple goodness am allowed conceive when young mother made him little coat these coats seem last long time though you renew them hannah did year year pattern effect are about same these clothes they shall wear when you are dead they shall wear them distant lands old family style shall show itself many places times what sort clothes are you making your children you are some expense pains matter you give good deal thought garb your household but how after all will they appear their vesture wisdom folly true beauty goodness poor imitation drapers they overcome same shall clothed white raiment are you educating your children overcome world its evil ways its pernicious usages overcome fear man servility gain overcome spirit hatred nations society among individuals so works everywhere corrupting morals well captivating tastes our young people then are you dressing your children take their places snowy lustrous throng compose throne most high we read one who cast out certain place because had not suitable garment god even now gathering elect four quarters earth calls great good truthful earnest common festival love are you making little coat your son may also join company those who are ushering kingdom god here hope enjoy its rewards hereafter paul speaking heavenly vesture uses expression if so being clothed we shall not found naked we would not unclothed adds spirit susceptible clothing flesh you all help furnish those garments not more do persons differ one than other you shall fin